  <acronym>SOLAR</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open-label Randomized Multi-center Phase III Study of TAS-118 Plus Oxaliplatin Versus S-1 Plus Cisplatin as First-line Therapy in Patients With Advanced Gastric Cancer</official_title>
