  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to evaluate the efficacy of TAS-118 plus Oxaliplatin compared
      with S-1 plus Cisplatin in overall survival in patients with advanced gastric cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
